, while Tyrion makes an important discovery.',65,'Alex Graves'),(5,1,'The Wars to Come','12-Apr-15',8.5,'Cersei and Jaime adjust to a world without Tywin. Tyrion and Varys arrive at Pentos. In Meereen, a new enemy emerges. Jon is caught between two kings.',53,'Michael Slovis'),(5,2,'The House of Black and White','19-Apr-15',8.5,'Arya arrives in Braavos. Jaime takes on a secret mission. Ellaria Sand seeks revenge for Oberyn\'s death. Stannis makes Jon a generous offer as the Night\'s Watch elects a new Lord Commander. Daenerys is faced with a difficult decision.',56,'Michael Slovis'),(5,3,'High Sparrow','26-Apr-15',8.5,'Tommen and Margaery wed. Arya has trouble adapting to her new life. Littlefinger reveals his plans to Sansa. Jon gives his first orders as Lord Commander. Tyrion and Varys arrive in Volantis.',60,'Mark Mylod'),(5,4,'Sons of the Harpy','3-May-15',8.7,'Jorah Mormont sets sail alongside his prisoner, Tyrion. Cersei makes a move against the Tyrells. Jaime and Bronn sneak into Dorne. Ellaria and the Sand Snakes make their plans. Melisandre tempts Jon. The Harpies attack.',51,'Mark Mylod'),(5,5,'Kill the Boy','10-May-15',8.6,'Daenerys arrests the heads of Meereen\'s great families. Jon makes a difficult decision. Theon is forced to face Sansa. Stannis rides south. Tyrion and Jorah enter the ruins of Old Valyria.',57,'Jeremy Podeswa'),(5,6,'Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken','17-May-15',8,'Arya is put to the test. Tyrion and Jorah are captured by slavers. Loras Tyrell is judged by the Sparrows. Jaime and Bronn face the Sand Snakes. Sansa marries Ramsay Bolton.',54,'Jeremy Podeswa'),(5,7,'The Gift','24-May-15',9,'Jon heads east as trouble begins to stir for Sam and Gilly at Castle Black. Sansa asks Theon for help. Tyrion and Jorah are sold as slaves. Cersei savors her triumph over the Tyrells as new plots are developed in the shadows.',59,'Miguel Sapochnik'),(5,8,'Hardhome','31-May-15',9.9,'Tyrion advises Daenerys. Sansa forces Theon to tell her a secret. Cersei rema